des: The Unofficial NBA Team Rosters skill can answer your questions about teams and players such as team rosters and player info including age, jersey number, position, weight, height, college, and salary. It can even answer your questions about who get paid most, who're the oldest, youngest, tallest, shortest, heaviest, and lightest players.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
